36
00:01:45,540 --> 00:01:47,610
trade and North Korea.

37
00:01:47,610 --> 00:01:48,650
On the trade front,

38
00:01:48,650 --> 00:01:50,650
the Trump administration has in the past

39
00:01:50,650 --> 00:01:53,380
accused China of unfair business practices,

40
00:01:53,380 --> 00:01:54,730
currency manipulation,

41
00:01:54,730 --> 00:01:56,870
and intellectual property theft.

42
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:57,870
In fact,

43
00:01:57,870 --> 00:02:01,270
blaming China was a true Trump campaign classic.

44
00:02:01,270 --> 00:02:06,370
We can’t allow China to rape our country,

45
00:02:06,370 --> 00:02:07,810
and that’s what they’re doing.”

46
00:02:07,810 --> 00:02:09,910
