56
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,300
Details are still a bit sparse,

57
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:39,300
and some of those deals

58
00:02:39,300 --> 00:02:40,630
had already been in the works

59
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:42,380
long before the meeting.

60
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:45,450
And some of them were just memorandums of
understanding,

61
00:02:45,450 --> 00:02:47,030
and not contracts.

62
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:48,030
But still,

63
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:50,090
250 billion is a lot of dough.

64
00:02:50,090 --> 00:02:52,930
That’s like Trump’s net worth times...

65
00:02:52,930 --> 00:02:54,790
uh, we’ll get back to you on that.

66
00:02:54,790 --> 00:02:58,170
Anyway, let’s take a look at some of the
deals.

67
00:02:58,170 --> 00:03:01,110
There was a $37 billion dollar deal with Boeing

68
00:03:01,110 --> 00:03:03,730
