124
00:05:24,889 --> 00:05:27,570
But there was one interesting thing.

125
00:05:27,570 --> 00:05:30,310
The day before President Trump landed in China,

126
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:32,449
he declared a new holiday,

127
00:05:32,449 --> 00:05:34,990
the National Day for the Victims of Communism.

128
00:05:34,990 --> 00:05:36,850
It “marks 100 years since

129
00:05:36,850 --> 00:05:39,550
the Bolshevik Revolution took place in Russia,”

130
00:05:39,550 --> 00:05:41,710
which gave us the Soviet Union.

131
00:05:41,710 --> 00:05:43,880
Since then, “communist totalitarian regimes

132
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,650
around the world have killed more than

133
00:05:45,650 --> 00:05:46,979
100 million people

134
00:05:46,979 --> 00:05:49,480
and subjected countless more to exploitation,

135
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:52,600
violence, and untold devastation.”

136
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,260
The White House said that the holiday was

137
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:55,949
to “remember those who have died

138
00:05:55,949 --> 00:05:59,540
and all who continue to suffer under communism.”

139
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:00,540
So in other words,

140
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:02,600
